Create a digital love poem for your boyfriend, girlfriend, fiancé, fiancee, husband or wife only using Applet technology. This can be real or imaginary. 

To accomplish this.

Create a single class called “LovePoem”

1) Use the image file named “roses.jpg” as the background. The image should be reduced 50% in size compared to the original size.

2) When the Applet loads, there should be a background sound. use the “slideflute.wav” file for the sound. Make sure the sound plays continuously unless the digital poem is closed.

3) Write an inspirational poem to your love one on the digital card. The poem should be maximum 5 sentences.

Grade (10 Points)

Note: Be creative especially with your design, font size, font type, text location, text color, etc. 